<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>466</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw kan Bawipa hi hmun thiang ah thitum biakam feh ter awkah kan ra,
 Kan cohlang law, samhri sih in, Nun chung nguh in biakam fek kan tuah lai.

[C1]
   Na dawtnak hri in run kan tem law, hohmanh nih then khawh lomi kan
   siter, Na van thluachuah run kan pe ko. Aa dawhmi inn-chungkhar si ve
   dingin.

[V2]
 Hi vawlei ah kan ton laimi zeizong kip ah kan i dawtnak hmun seh,
 Zawnruah dawtnak lungthin karh in, Dawt tlak lomi daw khotu kan siter.

[C2]
   Na dawtnak hri in run kan tem law, hohmanh nih then khawh lomi kan
   siter, Na van thluachuah run kan pe ko. Aa dawhmi inn-chungkhar si ve
   dingin.

[V3]
 Maw kan Bawipa na hmai ka ah thit-umnak cu hmaizahnak in kan tuah, Kan
 cohlang in, kan thianter ko, Vawlei thawkka i na timh cia bang khan.

[C3]
   Na dawtnak hri in run kan tem law, hohmanh nih then khawh lomi kan
   siter, Na van thluachuah run kan pe ko. Aa dawhmi inn-chungkhar si ve
   dingin.</lyrics>
<key>A</key>
<title>MO PUAI HLA CH466</title>
</song>